data.description: Welcome to your ideal home! Featuring all-impact windows & doors, roof replaced in 2020. Main house has a comfortable 3bed/2bath layout, offering ample space. Additionally, there's a versatile 1bed/1bath unit that could be your in-law quarters, guest suite, or a creative space to fit your lifestyle.  Located just moments away from Calle Ocho, the vibrant Miracle Mile, downtown Miami, & University of Miami, you're at the heart of culture, entertainment, & education. The property sits on a spacious lot, ready for your vision, whether it's hosting memorable gatherings, creating a lush garden, or whatever your heart desires. Extraordinary opportunity to design your dream home in one of Miami's most sought-after neighborhoods. It's time to unlock its full potential & make it uniquely yours.
